## 流程图类型

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F01["玩家进入商城"] --> S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F02["浏览道具"]
    S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F02 --> S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F03{"检查余额"}
    S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F03 -->|"不足"| S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F04["提示余额不足\n购买按钮禁用"]
    S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F03 -->|"充足"| S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F05["选择支付方式"]
    S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F05 --> S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F06["扣款 + 道具到账"]
    S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F04 --> End1["结束"]
    S4-BIZ-PURCHASE-F06 --> End2["购买成功"]
```

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant P as 玩家
    participant UI as 前端商城
    participant SV as 后端服务
    participant ACC as 账户系统
    participant DB as 数据库
    P->>UI: 点击购买
    UI->>SV: POST /order/create
    SV->>DB: 查询余额
    DB-->>SV: 返回余额
    SV->>ACC: 冻结余额
    ACC-->>SV: 冻结成功
    SV->>ACC: 扣减
    ACC-->>SV: 扣减成功
    SV->>DB: 创建订单
    DB-->>SV: 订单成功
    SV-->>UI: 购买成功
    UI-->>P: 道具到账 + 弹窗
```

